I transitioned from a sales role to corporate and am so much happier now. I believe you must be passionate about your day to day tasks in order to stay motivated throughout the workday. I also strongly believe that you must “know where you stand” with your leadership and feel supported in order to be fully engaged throughout the day and make steps toward future career goals. I believe passion, purpose, and strong leadership make for a happy and healthy employee, physically, mentally and financially.
